Dudu,is,a,multilingual,social,network,that,offers,a,translation,technology,that,allows,users,speaking,different,languages,to,communicate,freely,by,translating,phrases,from,one,language,into,another,in,real,time,Dudu,offers,a,simple,API,for,the,integration,of,Dudu,services,into,other,applications,Example,API,methods,include,FriendsList,worldEventCreate,changeAvatar,setPageTitle,and,more